<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="isdigit" id="isdigit">isdigit</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Синтаксис:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cctype&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">isdigit</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">int</span> ch <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

Функция isdigit() возвращяет ненулевое значение если её аргумент является цифрой. Иначе возвращает ноль.
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">     <span class="kw4">char</span> c<span class="sy4">;</span>
     <span class="kw3">scanf</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;%c&quot;</span>, <span class="sy3">&amp;</span>c <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
     <span class="kw1">if</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw3">isdigit</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span>c<span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span>
       <span class="kw3">printf</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;You entered the digit %c<span class="es1">\n</span>&quot;</span>, c <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
